title: Top 30 Country Aug 12, 2014
description:
Not a whole lot of movement on the charts so far in August, which is par for the course as many radio station Program Directors or Music Directors have been taking time off over the last month to enjoy some summer vacation.  We say hello to Scotty McCreery and David Nail at # 29 and 30 respectively and goodbye to Chris Young and Tyler Farr.  

Here are the Top 30 U.S. Country singles according to Mediabase for the week of August 12, 2014 in mp3 320 CBR Stereo.
